shortest independent\nvectors problem. A notion of dominant solutions is developed together with a\nsuitable lattice-reduction-based algorithm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Aug 2011 13:08:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 24 Oct 2012 13:25:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 3 Jul 2013 19:55:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-19"}
