th\nthe result of Flammia {\\it et al.} [Phys. Rev. Lett. 103, 261601 (2009)]. Some\nresults for the gapless limit $R^{\\rm KP}_n(t\\to 0)$ are discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Aug 2011 13:26:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 23 Dec 2011 16:48:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-02-13"}
